      "name": "Sticky Note1"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔄 Workflow Steps\n\n1. WEBHOOK TRIGGER\n   Receives POST with:\n   {\"topic\": \"...\", \"tone\": \"...\"}\n\n2. GEMINI AI\n   Writes a LinkedIn post with:\n   - Strong hook first line\n   - 3-5 short paragraphs\n   - Relevant emojis\n   - Hashtags at the end\n\n3. GOOGLE SHEETS\n   Saves the post as a draft row:\n   Date, Topic, Post content, Status",
        "height": 384,
        "width": 272,
        "color": 7
      },
